  "excerpt": "<p>Tips and Troubleshooting for using Healthcare.gov, including applying for an enrolling in health coverage.</p>",
  "content": "<p>Need help with your Health Insurance Marketplace\u00ae application?</p><ul class=\"ds-c-list\"><li><a href=\"/tips-and-troubleshooting/creating-an-account\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"a6cbcfb3-30f3-4121-9bb8-d04720f10e3a\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37476\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Creating an account\">Creating an account</a></li><li><a href=\"/tips-and-troubleshooting/logging-in\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"963ec5a2-3f30-41c7-8fb3-50a2fcc2f0ed\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37481\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Logging in to your account\">Logging into your account</a> \u2014 including what to do if you forgot your username, password, or the answers to your security questions</li><li><a href=\"/tips-and-troubleshooting/uploading-documents\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"7eefd611-a2df-4757-ab64-2badbd272c9d\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37486\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Uploading documents\">Uploading documents</a></li><li><a href=\"/tips-and-troubleshooting/browsers-and-settings\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"56d7892a-e335-4f4c-a9f4-1fdbaa7a0932\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37471\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Web browser, cookie &amp; cache settings\">Adjusting browser settings</a> \u2014 including cache and cookies</li></ul><h2>Can\u2019t find what you\u2019re looking for?</h2><ul class=\"ds-c-list\"><li>Visit our <a href=\"/get-answers\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"1204165e-6281-45d5-bfc8-c966812fe894\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"39366\" data-entity-bundle=\"landing_page\" title=\"How can we help you?\">Get Answers page</a> for help on popular topics</li><li><a href=\"/contact-us\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"2839b07e-0a5b-48bd-8fa4-ba9908d08200\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"39406\" data-entity-bundle=\"landing_page\" title=\"Contact us\">Contact the Marketplace Call Center</a></li><li>Want in-person assistance? <a href=\"https://localhelp.healthcare.gov/\">Find a trained helper near you.</a></li></ul><h2>More answers: Tips &amp; troubleshooting</h2><dl class=\"accordion learn-accordion\"><dt class=\"accordion-title\">Where can I find my Marketplace application?</dt><dd class=\"accordion-content\"><ol class=\"ds-c-list\"><li><a href=\"/login\">Log into your Marketplace account</a>.</li><li>Select your current application.</li></ol></dd></dl><dl class=\"accordion learn-accordion\"><dt class=\"accordion-title\"><span>What if I think I'm a victim of fraud related to the Marketplace?</span></dt><dd class=\"accordion-content\"><p>To learn to identify, report, and protect yourself from fraud, visit <a href=\"/how-can-i-protect-myself-from-fraud-in-the-health-insurance-marketplace\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"2ed6bb44-ae5a-456e-a74b-3dc0ab92d032\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36081\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Protect yourself from Marketplace fraud &amp; scams\">Protect yourself from Marketplace fraud.</a></p></dd></dl>",
